  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677000/extras/a363eb192115d14b128ff4e7856f5dc6.avif?t=1743057643\" width=616 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Charge... keep charging... and then jump! Make inertia your friend and fly! But not actually, as you might go too far and fall!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Chester the frog was looking at the newspaper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There was usually nothing interesting in the news.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But there was nothing interesting in Chester's wallet either...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suddenly, Chester spotted an ad for a good-paying job!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just test the [Rocket Boot Prototype] and strike it rich!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Game Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold a button to charge up and release to jump!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Calculate your height and overcome all obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the momentum of the bowling ball to your advantage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Gameplay Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-A challenging platformer!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Charge the rocket boots to elevate your jumps!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Wrestle against the weight of the magnetic bowling ball!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Each Level gets more difficult the farther you go!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Learn you can become a patient person by finding the patience you didn't know you had!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Between 1 and ∞ hours of frustrating gameplay!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Collect Infrognito Outfits!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Collect Music CDs and Dr. Toad Tokens!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Bonus unlockables at the end!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677000/extras/50fed414992f63a81e9e9a96a368ca21.avif?t=1743057643\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677000/extras/a363eb192115d14b128ff4e7856f5dc6.avif?t=1743057643\" width=616 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Charge... keep charging... and then jump! Make inertia your friend and fly! But not actually, as you might go too far and fall!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Chester the frog was looking at the newspaper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There was usually nothing interesting in the news.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But there was nothing interesting in Chester's wallet either...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suddenly, Chester spotted an ad for a good-paying job!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just test the [Rocket Boot Prototype] and strike it rich!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Game Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold a button to charge up and release to jump!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Calculate your height and overcome all obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the momentum of the bowling ball to your advantage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Gameplay Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-A challenging platformer!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Charge the rocket boots to elevate your jumps!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Wrestle against the weight of the magnetic bowling ball!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Each Level gets more difficult the farther you go!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Learn you can become a patient person by finding the patience you didn't know you had!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Between 1 and ∞ hours of frustrating gameplay!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Collect Infrognito Outfits!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Collect Music CDs and Dr. Toad Tokens!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Bonus unlockables at the end!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2677000/extras/50fed414992f63a81e9e9a96a368ca21.avif?t=1743057643\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p>",
